title: OTP verification for Tatkal bookings in 13 Central Railway trains from Saturday
description: Come December 6 and there will be a new OTP-based authentication system for ticket bookings under the Tatkal quota in select trains operated by the Central Railway. This marks the beginning of a small but significant change that wants to ensure proper use of the Tatkal tickets and prevent their misuse.
